Author: Andrew O. Finley [aut, cre],
  Sudipto Banerjee [ctb],
  Abhirup Datta [ctb],
  Paul B. May [ctb]
Maintainer: Andrew O. Finley <finleya@msu.edu>
Description: Bayesian linear mixed models with fixed effects, iid grouped
    random effects, and composable structured latent process terms. Current
    process terms include AR1, dense Gaussian process, nearest-neighbor
    Gaussian process, proper and Leroux CAR, ordered DAGAR, separable CAR-time,
    and covariate-scaled variants. The package uses a sparse precision
    formulation with post-fit latent process recovery, fitted values, and
    prediction.
URL: https://github.com/finleya/stLMM, https://finleya.github.io/stLMM/
